                     <title xml:lang="per" key="work_21783">گشائش نامه</title>
                     <note>
                        <p>Treatise on the ethics of kingship in refined prose and poetry, entitled <title>Gushāʾish'nāmah</title> by <persName key="person_f7235" role="aut">Khvājah Rāj Kiran</persName>, written at the suggestion of a certain <persName key="person_f7443" role="oth">Nand Lāl</persName> the munshī 
                        </p>
                        <p>Defective at beginning 
</p>
                        <p>Dated colophon (f. 97v): completed in the reign of <persName key="person_f7131" role="scr">Ghāz[ī] al-Dīn Ḥaydar Bahādur</persName>, 22 Rabīʿ al-S̲ānī 1238/6 January 1823 
                        </p>
                        <p>Roughly and, occasionally, inaccurately transcribed in Indian taʿlīq
</p>
                        <p>Damaged by wormholes and poor preservation; fragile
</p>
